name: Henry Smith
description: I am lost without you. I am seeking a marriage partner to live out the rest of our days, enjoying what time GOD bestows upon us. I don’t want games or non-sense just love and giving love to my God given woman. I love to travel and have fun, and will always have time for you no matter what! I want to make you happy because I know you will make me happy PLEASE NO SCAMMERS!!! I WANT A REAL caring woman, HAVE BEEN THRU THAT B/S BEFORE AND AM TIRED OF IT!!! IF THAT IS YOUR GAME , FIND SOMEONE ELSE!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!! BTW- you will get rejected really fast and never hear from me!!!!
